{"tid":1502444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老打爛人手機","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:53:01.000Z","uid":216002,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be5f9894ecd210d6267d91f8f9298b389857337c","tid":1502444,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"岩先搭西鐵 去緊錦上路個陣<br />\n有個廢老見到手足同佢政見唔一樣 就突然著火扔爛佢電話 仲鬧屌你老母 死廢青 到手足遠離佢 落左陣 個廢老都仲要覺得自己岩 大大聲講 邊個再講就打邊個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係到同大家講 搭車小心啲 啲廢老同狗一樣 情緒控制唔到嫁 同埋文宣要做好啲</span><br />\n<br />\n附上廢老圖兩張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJGFiOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJGFiOu.png&h=169fcde8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSEjzm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSEjzm7.png&h=9fdefb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老住天水圍 天耀個邊<br />\n<br />\n我知有好多手足都見到咩事 仲有人錄左片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條廢老唔係諗住咁屌人老母 又扔爛人手機 可以冇事啊"},{"pid":"afe71df39f4d2a63e29e85565dd2e90082af5684","tid":1502444,"uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:18:55.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c85a28f8b9116b1835e434e00d6ef854fe981e05","tid":1502444,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"廢老賠電話"},{"pid":"1d36e0bf94266a309da0a8e1562fc65092b715dd","tid":1502444,"uid":29093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"畀人打爛手機  都可以唔還拖 ?"},{"pid":"45b60fad609c47833ccabe17c9a0fa28f5b330b9","tid":1502444,"uid":213217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"廢老唔識法律， 影佢話你而家做野有可能成罪證。"},{"pid":"2d5aaa04a3df22708b0bd2caddb57a06d6f763f9","